data.description: Beautifully renovated showplace! This is the Rose model with the walls down. New flooring remodeled kitchen and baths, just ready for the next owner to move in,  relax and enjoy. The roof was replaced in 2009, A/C only 6 years old. New Plantation shutters, window treatments, and more.  So many special features about this home. Even the lakeview covered patio is oversized. Click on the 3 D tour to see what a special home this is.
